  ('Kervan Turkish Restaurant', '케르반 터키 레스토랑', '120 Itaewon-ro, Yongsan-gu, Seoul', '서울특별시 용산구 이태원로 120', 37.5345, 126.9858, 'WGS84', 'turkish', 2, 1, 'Authentic Turkish restaurant near Itaewon. Serves kebabs, pide, and Turkish tea. Halal-certified.', '{}', true, 0),
